  ('dietitian-moex-09056', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種餐飲服務需貫徹Q.S.C.V.H.D原則，以提升品質？', '["將中央廚房預處理的食物在店中迅速加熱（10~15分），其餐食品質與用餐環境佳者", "便宜、菜單多變化、服務好，適合團聚、家聚、小聚，在舒適環境享受用餐樂趣者", "設備講究之飲食店，高價位、菜單精緻且多變化、服務與環境好、氣氛佳者", "便宜、菜單多變化、美味與份量足，衛生安全，可大量生產、降低成本、製造過程注意衛生安全及良好 的品質控制者"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09057', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '製作50份綜合水果冰，雪花冰300元、芒果400元、西瓜210元、奇異果170元、草莓醬汁100元、果糖 80元，已知食物成本百分比為35%，人事水電費20%，則一份綜合水果冰售價為多少元？', '["46元", "72元", "125元", "187元"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09058', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關烹調對高麗菜影響之敘述，何者正確？', '["烹調時間長，會增加HS的產生量，所以適合高溫短時間烹調 2", "當吸收水分多時，易產生糊化作用，所以只要有充足水分，高溫短時間烹調即可", "在酸性環境中烹調會變黃，鹼性下會變更脆白", "烹調時間長，可增加SO 的散失量，所以適合長時間烹調 2"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09059', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關工作簡化之目的，何者正確？', '["以提升員工素質為原則", "增加工作效率進而提高產品的出產率", "提昇工作者勞力支出的表現，以作為節省成本之依據", "主要在提昇設備的效能，使廚房應用工具能物盡其用"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09060', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', 'HACCP系統雖是設計來預防所鑑定出之危害不會發生，但並不是在執行時都是這麼理想完美無缺。有時會 因不可預知的原因使CCP控制發生偏離。故應事先建立下列何種系統以茲預防？', '["建立記錄系統", "HACCP系統確認", "建立矯正措施", "執行管制監測"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09061', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是食品衛生管理工作所需採取之措施？', '["抽驗", "教育", "驗收", "審查"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09062', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種方式可以提升李氏手工蒸餃員工的工作效率，並增加產出量？', '["工作檯高度調整在75~80公分範圍", "員工工作椅子的高度在55~60公分範圍", "每位員工工作台操作範圍在以肩為中心之整個手臂為半徑所達到的範圍", "員工動作之操作過程中，連續以直線動作較佳"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09063', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-ad4b6c8a', 'sub-dietitian-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '餐廳廚房應撲滅或防止鼠、蠅、蟑螂等病媒侵入，否則容易得到下列何種污染問題？', '["金黃色葡萄球菌", "沙門氏菌", "肉毒桿菌", "大腸桿菌"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f49438bcf6e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097140", "c": "113", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "團體膳食設計與管理", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試、法醫師考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
